quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  23,76,"Soni chisimu Uwwe twakwembekenye ŵanganyao ni ilagasyo, nambo nganalitulusya kwa Ambuje ŵao, nambo soni nganaŵenda mwakulinandiya."
  23,77,"Kwikanila ndema jatuchaugulila nnango wana ilagasyo yaukali nnope, pajele ndemajo ŵanganyao tachiŵa ŵakata tama."
  23,78,"Soni Jwalakwe ni Ajula juŵan’guumbiile kupikana, kulola ni mitima (jaganichisya). Nambo kutogolela kwenu kuŵele kwannonope."
  24,58,"E jenumanja ŵankulupilile! Ampoposyeje aŵala ŵagapatile makono genu gakun’dyo (achikapolo ŵachilume ni ŵachikongwe ŵakwe) kwisa soni aŵala ŵanganaiche pakulisagamilila mwa jenumanja (alukosyo pa) ndema sitatu; nkanijiŵe swala ja Fajr, ni pandema jankuwulaga iwaalo yenu muusi (kuti nlijongole), kwisa soni panyuma pa swala ja Isha, (asi ni) ndema sitatu sya chiŵako chenu. Pangali ulemwa kukwenu kapena kukwao panyuma (pandema) syalakwesi (kwinjila mwangali kupoposya). (Ŵanganyao ali) ŵakunsyungulasyungula ŵanganyammwe, ŵane mwa jenumanja pa (kwatumichila) ŵane. Iyyoyopeyo Allah akusalichisya kukwenu ma Ȃya. Soni Allah ni Jwakumanyilila nnope, Jwalunda lwakusokoka."
  24,59,"Soni ŵanache mu jenumanja (achingosyo) pati ayiche ndema jakulisagamilila, basi apoposyeje (ndema syosope) yaakutiji pakupoposya aŵala ŵapaujo pao (ŵachikulile ŵao). Iyyoyopeyo Allah akusalichisya kukwenu ma Ȃya Gakwe. Soni Allah ni Jwakumanyilila nnope, Jwalunda lwakusokoka."
  24,60,"Soni achakongwe ŵajumu (ligongo lya uchekulu) aŵala ŵangakwembecheya kulombedwa, basi chipaŵe pangali ulemwa kukwao kuliunukula nguo syao (syapachanya) nambo mwangali kulosya ipeto (yankati mpela nkufu ibangili ni ine). Nambo naga ali atite aligose (ni kuleka kuliunukula nguo syao syapachanya) mpaka iŵe yambone nnope kukwao. Sano Allah ni Jwakupikanichisya, Jwakumanyilila nnope."
  25,22,"Lisiku lyatachigaona malaika kuchiŵa kwangali kusengwa lyele lisikulyo kwaakuleŵa, ni gachiŵecheta (malaikago kuti): “Kuŵele kwakusiŵilidwa kusyene (kwa jenumanja lelo kupata yambone).”"
  25,23,"Ni tuuchiiŵichilila itendo (yambone) yaŵapanganyisye ni tuuchiitenda kuŵa luwundu lwakuwululusyidwa."
  25,24,"Ŵandu ŵa ku Mbepo lyele lisikulyo tachikola malo gambone nnope gakutamilichika ni malo gambone nnope gagusama."